<title>Solving mode</title>

<p> When in "solving" mode, you can:</p>
<list>
	<item><p> Solve the puzzle manually by drawing on the grid</p></item>
	<item><p> Check your progress for errors</p></item>
	<item><p> Let the computer solve the puzzle (if it can!)</p></item>
	<item><p> Save a partially finished puzzle</p></item>
	<item><p> Reveal the solution by switching back to setting mode</p></item>
</list>
